column2: select school, floor (schoolyear/#) as fyear, avg (absent) as absent, avg (enrolled) as enrolled , avg (cast (absent as real) )/avg (cast (enrolled as real) ) as frAbsent from schoolattendance group by school, floor (schoolyear/#) ) , r as (select sl.location as location , a.* from a join schoollocation sl on sl.fiscal_year = a.fyear and sl.ATS_SYSTEM_CODE = a.school and sl.LOCATION_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION like #) select mz._id, max (mz.location.ToString () ) as zLoc , sum (r.absent) /sum (r.enrolled) as fAbsent from MSchoolZones mz join r on mz.location.STContains (r.location) = # mz._year = r.fyear group by mz._id
